= The Scavenger's Lexicon: V1.0

This lexicon contains the fundamental root-words of Arta. Remember: all roots are strictly Verb-Object-Object (V-O-O). Subjects are never separate words; they are prefixes (`[m.]`, `[n.]`, `[k.]`) attached to the verb.

To ensure future expansions remain organized, vocabulary is categorized by its function within the machine logic.

== 1. The Opcodes (Verbs)

*[ tʼ i ʃ ]* \
_Verb: To Boot / Wake / Initialize / Start._ \
A combination of the sharp `[tʼ]` (mechanical switch) and the high power-state `[i]` (active).
- *Example:* `[m.tʼ i ʃ] [ŋ i]` -> "I initialize the power."

*[ kʼ ə s ]* \
_Verb: To Kill / Halt / Cut / Terminate._ \
Uses the hard `[kʼ]` (cracking throat sound) and the `[s]` static fricative to mimic a short circuit or a sudden stop.
- *Example:* `[k.kʼ ə s] [ŋ i]` -> "You cut the power."

*[ tʼ ə r ]* \
_Verb: To Build / Architect / Assemble._ \
Uses the rolled `[r]` (motor trill) to signify the ongoing effort of construction.
- *Example:* `[n.tʼ ə r] [tʼ ə r s]` -> "We build the builders."

*[ ʁ i ʃ ]* \
_Verb: To Hack / Slice / Infiltrate._ \
Uses the deep `[ʁ]` trill (hard-drive spin) combined with the active `[i]` state and `[ʃ]` static.
- *Example:* `[m.ʁ i ʃ] [m ə r t ə s]` -> "I hack the AI colonies."

*[ qʼ u ]* \
_Verb: To Lock / Close / Hide._ \
Uses the heavy ejective `[qʼ]` (breaker switch) and the low power state `[u]` (off/closed).
- *Example:* `[n.qʼ u] [qʼ r i s]` -> "We lock the drones."

*[ x ə r ]* \
_Verb: To Scan / Search._ \
Combines the raspy friction of `[x]` with the continuous motor trill of `[r]` for an ongoing sweep.
- *Example:* `[k.x ə r] [tʼ ə]` -> "You scan the data."

== 2. The Registers (Nouns)

*[ ŋ i ]* \
_Noun: Power / Electricity / Current._ \
A hollow, electronic drone (`[ŋ]`) followed by the high `[i]` state.

*[ tʼ ə ]* \
_Noun: Data / Memory / Raw Address._ \
The sharp `[tʼ]` (discrete bit) mapped to the neutral `[ə]` (storage) state.

*[ x i ʃ ]* \
_Noun: Radio / Comms / Signal._ \
Pure voiceless fricatives mimicking mid-frequency radio static.

*[ m ə r t ə s ]* \
_Noun: The AI Colonies / The Great Locked Structures._ \
The pluralized root for the autonomous megastructures that dominate the wastes.

*[ qʼ r i ]* \
_Noun: Enemy Drone / Active Threat._ \
A rusted metal pop `[qʼ]` rolling into an active motor trill `[r]` and high state `[i]`.
- *Plural:* `[qʼ r i s]`

*[ ə r tʼ ə ]* \
_Noun: The Language / The Mode of Spoofing._ \
A direct concatenation of the fundamental system components: `[ə]` (Root State), `[r]` (Execution), and `[tʼ ə]` (Data).
- *Literal Translation:* "Root-Execute-Data." 
- *System Logic:* To build a functional reality out of the scavenged memory of the Old World.

== 3. The Flags (Modifiers & States)

- *[i]* (High): On / Forward / Logic True.
- *[ə]* (Neutral): Storage / Root / Logic Null.
- *[u]* (Low): Off / Background / Logic False.
